                <footer>
                    <p>Powered by the Neptune CMS, SaaS Edition</p><p><small>Copyright Â© 2012 StormDEV, All Rights Reserved<br>{$NeptuneCore->footer_timer()}<br>Using the {function="NeptuneSQL::type()"} database engine</small></p>
